acting columbia college dean henry coleman was held hostage 
during the revolt professor orest ranum lost a decades research 
when a protester torched his files 
later ted gold a member of the radical weather underground 
was killed when a homemade bomb exploded in a greenwich village 
townhouse in 1970 david gilbert is serving a 75year prison 
sentence for his role in a 1981 armed car robbery 
