with the first to come into service in 1996 
the estimated cost of each jet will be 49 million and some 
west german critics say that is too much 
younger said the european fighter aircraft will fulfill a 
vital defense need in the best and most costeffective way it will 
continue the trend of successful european collaboration in 
aerospace and it will ensure that our industry remains in the 
forefront of this technology to the end of the century and beyond 
