satisfy peoples needs and in some areas bread quality and 
assortment was poor the report said 
of the 15 soviet republics armenia had the worst record from 
january to march for fulfillment of industrial contract 
obligations armenian factories completed just 985 percent of 
their orders compared to a high of 999 percent for byelorussia 
and latvia 
