salaries improving household services or building schools 
hospitals and cultural centers 
during much of february many of armenias factories schools 
and businesses were closed in a strike prompted by an ethnic 
dispute 
the report was released as us intelligence agencies released 
in washington an assessment saying that gorbachevs reforms ran 
into serious obstacles in 1987 
